high_descs: Walk straight several steps, take a left towards the wall, and then turn right towards the microwave.
Open the left cabinet above the microwave and take out the cup from it.
Turn right and walk towards the sink on your left.
Place the cup in the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Turn left and find the coffee maker on the counter to your left.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Go forward, then turn left, then turn right to go to the microwave.
Take the mug from the cabinet to the left, above the microwave.
Turn right, go forward then turn left to face the sink.
Wash the mug in the sink.
Turn around, then turn right to go to the coffee maker on the counter.
Place the mug at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug at the coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk and stand in front of the red microwave you see to the left of the dishwasher.
Open the cupboard that's over the left side of the microwave and get the dirty mug that's up there..
Turn right and walk to the sink that will be on your left and then turn left to face it.
Wash the mug in the sink then get it back out and close the tap.
Turn left and walk to the wall then turn left to look at the coffee pot.
Put the mug under the coffee maker's spout.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug in the coffee maker.
